for each word found, 
	if doesnt exist in db, create a row for it and set count to 1,
	otherwise add 1 to the count of that word.
	go through all the other words in the given post and update the link table
		if the link doesnt exist in db, create row for it and set count to 1
		otherwise add 1 to the link
		
		
word
	id
	word
	count
	
link
	id
	word1
	word2
	count
